headline: BMO downgrades CSX as M&A upside already priced in
summary: Investing.com -- BMO Capital Markets downgraded CSX Corp (NASDAQ:CSX) to Market Perform from Outperform, saying the recent 20% rally in the rail operator’s stock has largely priced in potential takeover speculation, leaving a more balanced risk-reward profile.
